snippet.title: ‘Aquaman 2’ Petition to Remove Amber Heard Exceeds 1.6 Million Signees After Depp ‘Fantastic Beasts’
snippet.description:
An online petition calling on Warner Bros. to remove Amber Heard from the upcoming comic book tentpole “Aquaman 2” has garnered over 1.6 million signatures and is fast approaching the 2 million mark (via Deadline)  ...
